      title: `Talks (Part 2)`,
      description: `<b>탈중앙화 조직을 여행하는 히치하이커를 위한 안내서 - 사례로 알아보는 DAO (Panel Talk)</b><br>- Gen Lee, Junha, Duke (Uniswap Labs, Hyperithm, Myosin)<br><br><b>Summa: ZK Proofs of Solvency with Halo2</b><br>- Jinhwan Shin (Ethereum Foundation, PSE)<br><br><b>PSE: Level Up with Open Source</b><br>- Adrian Li (Ethereum Foundation, PSE)<br><br><b>ZKAP: Self-Custodial Recoverable Wallet</b><br>- Junghyun Kim (Team BaeRae)`
    },
    {
      time: '04:30 PM',
      title: `Talks (Part 3)`,
      description: `<b>Optimism 커뮤니티에 기여하는 법</b><br>- Hada Kang (Freelancer)<br><br><b>The best way: correct number of the statistics</b><br>- Jack Jin (Kaia Foundation)<br><br><b>Journey of Civic Hackers</b><br>- Jaewon Kim, Joonwon Lee, Minjun Kim (Bluenode, DSRV, Bifrost)`
    },
    {
      time: '06:00 PM',
      title: `Closing Remarks`,
    },
